  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      368.66,
      543.35,
      384.2
    ],
    "text": "water motor from the possession of Gamini Gunathilake who stated in evidence",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      392.8,
      404.86,
      408.34
    ],
    "text": "that he purchased the said water motor from Puspakumara.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      426.88,
      543.42,
      442.42
    ],
    "text": "Puspakumara in his evidence stated that the accused-appellant gave him the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      451.12,
      543.39,
      466.66
    ],
    "text": "water motor; that he sold it to Gamini Gunathilake for Rs.6000/-; and that he gave",
